document_data.History:
In [[1491 DR]], his home was besieged by [[demon]]s and their [[fire giant]] minions from [[Maerimydra]]. He identified the [[elemental codex]] in [[Earthfast]] as a powerful weapon that could defeat the invading army. So he went to ask the [[dwarves]] for the codex, but was immediately rejected. Afterward, Murssvayas hired [[Furgis Boltsmelter]] to get it by illegal means.{{Cite adventurers league/Boltsmelter's Book|18}}

Later, after the fall of Szith Morcane, he was chosen by the archmage [[Solom Ned'razak]] as his representative to hire an adventuring party in [[Elventree]] to save the [[drow]] alchemist [[Xaven Tanor'this]].{{Cite adventurers league/It's All in the Blood|8-9}}

After the presumed death of Solom, Murssvayas became the leader of the drow resistance to the invading [[fire giant]]s but his position was precarious.{{Cite adventurers league/Szith Morcane Unbound|14}}
